		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_omniknight_purification"	            "洗礼【凌霜圣地】"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_omniknight_purification_Description"	"立刻治疗范围内所有友方单位并对周围的所有敌方单位造成伤害。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_omniknight_purification_Lore"	        "全知的牧师们善于清除己方战士们身心中的污杂。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_omniknight_purification_heal"	        "治疗/伤害："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_omniknight_purification_radius"	        "伤害作用范围："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_omniknight_purification_cast_radius"	"治疗作用范围："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_omniknight_degen_aura"	                "恢复光环【凌霜圣地】"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_omniknight_degen_aura_Description"	    "全能骑士周围友方单位的移动速度、攻击力和恢复能力得到极大提升。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_omniknight_degen_aura_Note0"	        "对技能免疫单位无效。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_omniknight_degen_aura_Lore"	            "作为神圣的化身，普里斯特．雷霆之怒足以削弱那些不忠之徒。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_omniknight_degen_aura_radius"	        "作用范围："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_omniknight_degen_aura_speed_bonus"	    "%移动速度加成："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_omniknight_degen_aura_attack_bonus_tooltip"	"攻击力加成："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_omniknight_degen_aura_bonus_health_regen"	"恢复速度加成："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_frostivus2018_omniknight_degen_aura_effect"	        "恢复光环"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_huskar_burning_spear"	            "沸血之矛【凌霜圣地】"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_huskar_burning_spear_Description"	"哈斯卡的普通攻击点燃<font color='#70EA72'>他的目标和周围敌人</font>，持续造成伤害。多个攻击效果将产生额外伤害。每次攻击都会消耗哈斯卡的部分生命。伤害持续8秒。<font color='#70EA72'>烧灼伤害在第一次长矛击中后立刻生效。</font>"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_huskar_burning_spear_Lore"	        "神灵武士的武器经过自身鲜血的沾染，燃起了烈火 - 敌人将领受远超己痛的苦楚。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_huskar_burning_spear_Note0"	        "沸血之矛在多次施放到目标身上效果可以叠加。没有叠加上限。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_huskar_burning_spear_Note1"	        "哈斯卡不能使用此技能自杀。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_huskar_burning_spear_health_cost"	"生命消耗："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_huskar_burning_spear_burn_damage"	"燃烧伤害："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_huskar_burning_spear_spear_aoe"	"<font color='#70EA72'>烧灼作用范围：</font>"

		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_phantom_assassin_stifling_dagger_nb2017"	"窒息之刃(芳晓节)"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_phantom_assassin_stifling_dagger_nb2017_Description"	"<font color='#70EA72'>在目标地点周围投掷一阵匕首，每一把都会击中路径上的第一个单位。</font>匕首减缓敌人移动速度，造成%base_damage%+幻影刺客物理攻击的%attack_factor_tooltip%%%的物理伤害，并继承物品和技能的攻击特效。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_phantom_assassin_stifling_dagger_nb2017_Note0"	"如果攻击效果为几率触发，匕首的触发几率与原几率相同。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_phantom_assassin_stifling_dagger_nb2017_Lore"	"魅影之纱成员学习到的第一个技能，中招就意味着下一次攻击要来了。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_phantom_assassin_stifling_dagger_nb2017_move_slow"	"%移动速度减缓："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_phantom_assassin_stifling_dagger_nb2017_duration"	"减速持续时间："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_phantom_assassin_stifling_dagger_nb2017_base_damage"	"基础伤害："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_phantom_assassin_stifling_dagger_nb2017_attack_factor_tooltip"	"%攻击伤害："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_phantom_assassin_stifling_dagger_nb2017_dagger_count"	"匕首数量："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_phantom_assassin_stifling_dagger_nb2017_dagger_range"	"匕首距离："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_necrolyte_reapers_scythe_datadriven"	                    "死神镰刀"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_necrolyte_reapers_scythe_datadriven_Description"       	"眩晕目标敌方单位，然后造成基于他当前损失生命值的伤害。被死神镰刀杀死后下次复活时间将会增加%respawn_constant%秒。如果目标在死神镰刀效果下死亡，击杀者为瘟疫法师。\n\n可用神杖升级。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_necrolyte_reapers_scythe_datadriven_damage_per_health"	"每点损失生命值造成伤害："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_necrolyte_reapers_scythe_datadriven_stun_duration"	    "眩晕时间："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_necrolyte_reapers_scythe_datadriven_damage_per_health_scepter"  "神杖升级每点失去生命值造成伤害："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_necrolyte_reapers_scythe_datadriven_mana_cost_scepter"	"神杖升级魔法消耗："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_necrolyte_reapers_scythe_datadriven_cooldown_scepter"	    "神杖升级冷却时间："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_necrolyte_reapers_scythe_datadriven_aghanim_description"	"提高每点损失生命值造成的伤害，减少1级时的魔法消耗，减少1级和2级时的冷却时间。被死神镰刀击杀的单位无法买活。"
		 "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_clinkz_searing_arrows"	"灼热之箭【凌霜圣地】"
		 "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_clinkz_searing_arrows_Description"	"克林克兹的箭矢中注入了火焰，<font color='#70EA72'>并且对攻击目标后方的敌人造成溅射伤害。</font>"
		 "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_clinkz_searing_arrows_Lore"	"克林克兹用他的灼热精华点燃弓箭，造成毁灭性打击。"
		 "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_clinkz_searing_arrows_Note0"	"灼热之箭能对建筑造成伤害。"
		 "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_clinkz_searing_arrows_Note1"	"伤害直接作为物理伤害加到克林克兹的攻击伤害中。"
		 "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_clinkz_searing_arrows_damage_bonus"	"额外伤害："
		 "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_clinkz_searing_arrows_attack_spill_range"	"溅射攻击距离："
		 "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_clinkz_searing_arrows_attack_spill_width"	"溅射攻击宽度："
		 "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_clinkz_searing_arrows_spill_damage_multiplier"	"溅射伤害倍数："
		 "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_clinkz_wind_walk"	"骨隐步【凌霜圣地】"
		 "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_clinkz_wind_walk_Description"	"克林克兹进入隐身状态，可以穿过单位，攻击或使用技能将导致自己显形。<font color='#70EA72'>每次穿过单位可以临时窃取一部分攻击力。</font>"
		 "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_clinkz_wind_walk_Lore"	"随着火焰的爆裂和烟雾的升起，骷髅弓箭手的身形遁于无形。"
		 "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_clinkz_wind_walk_Note0"	"开启后不会打断大多数持续施法类技能和物品。"
		 "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_clinkz_wind_walk_Note1"	"渐隐时间为0.6秒。"
		 "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_clinkz_wind_walk_duration"	"持续时间："
		 "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_clinkz_wind_walk_move_speed_bonus_pct"	"%移动速度提升："
		 "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_clinkz_wind_walk_attack_steal_duration"	"攻击力窃取持续时间："
		 "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_clinkz_wind_walk_bonus_base_dmg_per_stack"	"每点能量攻击力："
		 "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_clinkz_wind_walk_max_stacks"	"最大叠加次数："
		 "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_frostivus2018_clinkz_wind_walk"	"骨隐步【凌霜圣地】"
		 "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_frostivus2018_clinkz_wind_walk_Description"	"这个单位是隐形的。"
		 "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_frostivus2018_clinkz_wind_walk_bonus_damage"	"骨隐步【凌霜圣地】"
		 "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_frostivus2018_clinkz_wind_walk_bonus_damage_Description"	"这个单位拥有额外攻击力。"
		 "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_frostivus2018_clinkz_wind_walk_attack_debuff"	"骨隐步【凌霜圣地】"
		 "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_frostivus2018_clinkz_wind_walk_attack_debuff_Description"	"这个单位的攻击力降低了。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_death_pact_datadriven"	"死亡契约"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_death_pact_datadriven_Description"	"克林克兹消化掉一个友方或敌方的非英雄单位，生命上限及攻击力增加，数值为目标一定百分比的生命值。\n<font color='#FF7800'>怪物血量按照普通难度计算。</font> \n<font color='#FF7800'>每关降低当前效果的5%.</font>"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_death_pact_datadriven_duration"	"持续时间："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_death_pact_datadriven_health_gain_pct"	"%生命提升："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_death_pact_datadriven_damage_gain_pct"	"%攻击力提升："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_death_pact_datadriven_Note0"	"如果目标是敌方单位，克林克兹将获得经验和金钱。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_death_pact_datadriven_Note1"	"克林克兹的当前血量和生命值上限都将提高。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_death_pact_datadriven_Note2"	"持续时间结束后，血量上限回到正常值，但是当前生命值不变（不会高于血量上限）。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_death_pact_datadriven_Lore"	"萨瑟雷克斯的死亡契约已经成了克林克兹的一部分，他通过杀死那些低等生物来使自己的枯骨获得新生。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_death_pact"	                "死亡契约"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_death_pact_Description"	    "攻击力和生命值均获得提升。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_pugna_ward_winter_2018"	                         "腐生守卫(凌霜圣地)"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_pugna_ward_winter_2018_Description"	             "帕格纳在目标地点放置一个腐生守卫。每次他们消耗魔法都会治疗友军。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_pugna_ward_winter_2018_aura_radius"	             "光环作用范围："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_pugna_ward_winter_2018_mana_multiplier"	         "每点魔法治疗生命："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_pugna_ward_winter_2018_aura_mana_regen"	         "光环魔法回复："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_pugna_ward_winter_2018_ward_duration"	             "守卫持续时间："
		"npc_dota_pugna_ward_winter_2018"                                        "腐生守卫"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_pugna_ward_winter_2018_effect"                    "腐生守卫光环"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dark_seer_wall_of_replica_nb2017"	                "复制之墙(暗月来袭)"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dark_seer_wall_of_replica_nb2017_Description"	    "制造一堵扭曲的光墙，对穿过的任意<font color='#70EA72'>敌方单位</font>造成减速，并复制一个其自身的幻象，幻象由黑暗贤者控制，<font color='#70EA72'>同一时间每个单位只会存在一个幻象。</font>幻象持续到光墙消失，或者被敌人消灭。\n\n可用神杖升级。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dark_seer_wall_of_replica_Lore"	                "尽管黑暗贤者不能回到他原来的国度，他仍然能召唤出一道具有强大心智力量的璀璨幻墙，在敌人之间制造混乱。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dark_seer_wall_of_replica_nb2017_Note0"	        "幻象和米波的克隆体不会产生幻象。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dark_seer_wall_of_replica_nb2017_Note1"	        "创造1000码长的光墙，光墙垂直于黑暗贤者和目标点的连线。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dark_seer_wall_of_replica_nb2017_duration"	    "墙体持续时间："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dark_seer_wall_of_replica_nb2017_tooltip_outgoing" "%复制体攻击力："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dark_seer_wall_of_replica_nb2017_tooltip_replica_total_damage_incoming"	"%复制体承受伤害："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dark_seer_wall_of_replica_nb2017_range_tooltip"	"施法距离："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dark_seer_wall_of_replica_nb2017_tooltip_outgoing_scepter"	"%神杖升级复制体攻击力："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dark_seer_wall_of_replica_nb2017_movement_slow"	"%移动速度减缓："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dark_seer_wall_of_replica_nb2017_slow_duration"	"减速持续时间："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_invoker_cold_snap_lua" "急速冷却"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_invoker_cold_snap_lua_Description" "祈求者将敌人的热量抽空，将其降到绝对零度。敌人将伤害并被短暂冻结，后续攻击同样会使敌人冻结并造成额外伤害。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_invoker_cold_snap_lua_Lore" "塞卓昂的无尽战栗。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_invoker_cold_snap_lua_Note0" "只有10点以上的实际伤害才能触发急速冷却。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_invoker_cold_snap_lua_duration" "急速冷却持续时间："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_invoker_cold_snap_lua_freeze_duration" "冻结时间："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_invoker_cold_snap_lua_freeze_damage" "冷却伤害："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_invoker_cold_snap_lua_freeze_cooldown" "冻结冷却时间："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_invoker_tornado_lua" "强袭飓风"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_invoker_tornado_lua_Description""释放出一道快速移动的飓风，将路径上的敌方单位卷起，使其在空中无助的漂浮一段时间，然后落地受死。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_invoker_tornado_lua_Lore" "托纳鲁斯之爪。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_invoker_tornado_lua_Note0" "被强袭飓风吹起时单位处于无敌状态，落地时受到伤害。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_invoker_tornado_lua_travel_distance" "最大距离："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_invoker_tornado_lua_area_of_effect" "作用范围："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_invoker_tornado_lua_lift_duration" "吹起时间："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_invoker_tornado_lua_base_damage" "基础伤害："

		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_invoker_ghost_walk_lua"								"幽灵漫步"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_invoker_ghost_walk_lua_Description"					"祈求者操纵冰雷之力围绕自身，使自己隐形。元素的组合会造成附近敌人的减速，并使祈求者自身移动速度减缓。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_invoker_ghost_walk_lua_self_slow"						"%自身速度变化："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_invoker_ghost_walk_lua_duration"						"持续时间："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_invoker_ghost_walk_lua_area_of_effect"				"作用范围："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_invoker_ghost_walk_lua_enemy_slow"					"%敌方减速："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_invoker_ghost_walk_lua_self"							"幽灵漫步"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_invoker_ghost_walk_lua_self_Description"				"隐身，移动速度变化%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_MOVESPEED_BONUS_PERCENTAGE%%%，并减速周围的敌人。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_invoker_ghost_walk_lua_enemy"						"幽灵漫步"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_invoker_ghost_walk_lua_enemy_Description"			"附近有鬼！移动速度被减缓%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_MOVESPEED_BONUS_PERCENTAGE%%%。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_invoker_ghost_walk_lua_Lore"							"米瑞特之阻碍。"
