		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_ranged_cleave"                     "双管霰弹枪"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_ranged_cleave_Description"         "<h1>被动: 霰弹</h1>仅限远程：在%cleave_radius%半径内造成%cleave_dmg%%%溅射伤害。获得 %bonus_range% 额外攻击距离。"
