		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_drow_ranger_marksmanship_lua_Lore"								"卓尔游侠是弓箭手登峰造极的典型。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_drow_ranger_marksmanship_lua_Note0"								"射手天赋会触发真实攻击。"
