		//Tidehunter
		//Timbersaw
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shredder_chakram_lua"								"锯齿飞轮"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shredder_chakram_lua_Description"					"伐木机将主锯刃射向目标区域，锯刃会高速旋转，对周围的敌方单位造成伤害。  在锯刃作用范围内的敌方单位每损失最大生命值的%slow_health_percentage%%%，他们的移动速度都会进一步被降低。锯刃在发射和收回的过程中都将造成伤害并砍倒碰到的树木。  在发射锯刃后伐木机将无法攻击，同时会持续消耗魔法。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shredder_chakram_lua_Lore"							"消灭植物的终极武器。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shredder_chakram_lua_Note0"							"如果伐木机魔法耗尽，或移动超出%break_distance%距离，则锯齿飞轮会返回。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shredder_chakram_lua_radius"							"范围："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shredder_chakram_lua_pass_damage"					"飞行伤害；"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shredder_chakram_lua_damage_per_second"				"每秒伤害："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shredder_chakram_lua_slow"							"%减速："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shredder_chakram_lua_mana_per_second"				"每秒消耗魔法："
		// "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shredder_chakram_lua_scepter_description"			"提供第二个锯齿飞轮。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shredder_chakram_lua_return"							"收回锯齿飞轮"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shredder_chakram_lua_return_Description"				"让伐木机收回锯齿飞轮。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shredder_chakram_2_lua"						"锯齿飞轮（二）"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shredder_chakram_2_lua_Description"			"伐木机将次锯刃射向目标区域，锯刃会高速旋转，对周围的敌方单位造成伤害。  在锯刃作用范围内的敌方单位每损失最大生命值的5%，他们的移动速度都会进一步被降低。锯刃在发射和收回的过程中都将造成伤害并砍倒碰到的树木。  在发射锯刃后伐木机将无法攻击，同时会持续消耗魔法。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shredder_chakram_2_lua_Lore"					"我砍砍砍砍砍砍砍砍砍！"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shredder_chakram_2_lua_Note0"					"如果伐木机魔法耗尽，或移动超出%break_distance%距离，则锯齿飞轮会返回。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shredder_chakram_2_lua_Note1"					"两个锯齿飞轮的减速效果不叠加。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shredder_chakram_2_lua_radius"					"范围："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shredder_chakram_2_lua_pass_damage"			"飞行伤害；"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shredder_chakram_2_lua_damage_per_second"		"每秒伤害："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shredder_chakram_2_lua_slow"					"%减速："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shredder_chakram_2_lua_mana_per_second"		"每秒消耗魔法："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shredder_chakram_lua_2_return"					"收回锯齿飞轮"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shredder_chakram_lua_2_return_Description"		"让伐木机收回锯齿飞轮。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_shredder_chakram_slow_lua"							"锯齿飞轮"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_shredder_chakram_slow_lua_Description"				"在一段时间内承受伤害并被锯齿飞轮减速。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_shredder_chakram_disarm_lua"						"锯齿飞轮解除武装"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_shredder_chakram_disarm_lua_Description"			"锯齿飞轮在空中时你无法攻击。"
		//Tinker
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tinker_heat_seeking_missile_lua"									"热导飞弹"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tinker_heat_seeking_missile_lua_Description"						"向%radius%范围内最近的可见单位发射飞弹。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tinker_heat_seeking_missile_lua_Lore"								"鲍什最后救下来的玩意儿，是一个改造过的制导式火箭筒。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tinker_heat_seeking_missile_lua_damage"							"伤害："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tinker_heat_seeking_missile_lua_targets"							"目标："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tinker_heat_seeking_missile_lua_speed"							"飞弹速度："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tinker_heat_seeking_missile_lua_ability_note"						"影响<font color='#B694FF'>普通单位</font>。"
		//Tiny
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tiny_tree_grab_lua"												"抓树"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tiny_tree_grab_lua_lore"											"木棍和石头就能让骨头散架，而建筑也将马上步其后尘。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tiny_tree_grab_lua_Description"									"抓起一棵树砸向敌人的头。可以使用一定次数，攻击距离得到提升,攻击造成更多伤害，并且路径上的单位受到全额溅射伤害。可以将树木扔出，对远距离的敌人造成攻击伤害。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tiny_tree_grab_lua_scepter_description"                           ""
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tiny_tree_grab_lua_attack_count"                                  "攻击次数："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tiny_tree_grab_lua_bonus_damage"									"伤害加成："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tiny_tree_grab_lua_bonus_damage_buildings"						"%建筑伤害加成："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tiny_tree_grab_lua_splash_pct"									"%溅射伤害："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tiny_tree_grab_lua_stun_duration"									"眩晕持续时间"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tiny_tree_grab_lua_attack_range"						   			"攻击范围："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tiny_tree_grab_lua_Note0"											"在扔出树木后冷却开始。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_tiny_grab_lua"													"抓树"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_tiny_grab_lua_Description"										"攻击造成更高伤害，且会溅射。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tiny_tree_throw_lua"												"扔树"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tiny_tree_throw_lua_Description"									"将树木扔向目标单位，触发自身对其的攻击，并且对周围目标造成溅射伤害。对主目标"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tiny_tree_throw_lua_Lore"											"就算是敌人也能分享小小对树木的热情。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tiny_tree_throw_lua_range"										"施法距离："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tiny_tree_throw_lua_splash_radius"								"溅射半径："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tiny_tree_throw_lua_movement_slow"								"%移动速度减缓："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tiny_tree_throw_lua_slow_duration"								"减速持续时间："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_tiny_tree_throw_lua_slow"		                                "扔树"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_tiny_tree_throw_lua_slow_Description"		                    "因树木的创伤，移动速度被减缓%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_MOVESPEED_BONUS_PERCENTAGE%%%%。"
		//Treant Protector
		//Troll Warlord
		// "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_troll_warlord_berserkers_rage_ability_note"       "与<font color='#B694FF'>抓树</font>互斥，无法同时选到"
		//Tusk
