		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_torture_pipe_2_datadriven_dot_amplify"				    "%+每点属性提升技能伤害"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shadow_fiend_requiem_of_souls_lua"                                "魂之挽歌"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shadow_fiend_requiem_of_souls_lua_Description"                    "影魔聚集捕获的灵魂，以多道魔能的形式释放。若距离影魔过近将受到数道魔能的伤害。敌方单位受到魂之挽歌伤害的同时会降低伤害输出，并且移动速度降低，持续%requiem_slow_duration%秒。<br><br>死亡时会自动释放魂之挽歌，不占用主动大招的冷却时间。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shadow_fiend_requiem_of_souls_lua_aghanim_description"            "提升支配死灵的灵魂上限，魂之挽歌可以回归影魔。回归的伤害波造成较低的伤害，但是影魔会回复与伤害值相等的生命。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shadow_fiend_requiem_of_souls_lua_ability_note"                   "不需要技能<font color='#B694FF'>支配死灵</font>。固定释放18道伤害波 (神杖升级后为23道)。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shadow_fiend_requiem_of_souls_lua_abilitycastpoint"               "施法延迟："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shadow_fiend_requiem_of_souls_lua_requiem_reduction_ms"           "%移动速度减少："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shadow_fiend_requiem_of_souls_lua_requiem_reduction_damage"       "%攻击力降低："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shadow_fiend_requiem_of_souls_lua_requiem_damage_pct_scepter"     "%神杖升级回归伤害："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shadow_fiend_requiem_of_souls_lua_requiem_heal_pct_scepter"       "%神杖升级回归时治疗量："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shadow_fiend_requiem_of_souls_lua_Lore"                           "那些死者的灵魂被捕获后尽数释放，毁灭他们生前的盟友。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shadow_fiend_requiem_of_souls_lua_Note0"                          "固定释放18道伤害波 (神杖升级后为23道)。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shadow_fiend_requiem_of_souls_lua_Note1"                          "魂之挽歌的移动速度减缓效果均无视技能免疫。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shadow_fiend_requiem_of_souls_lua_Note2"                          "死亡时释放的魂之挽歌不会施加恐惧和减速效果。"

		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_sandking_caustic_finale_lua"									         "腐尸毒"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_sandking_caustic_finale_lua_Description"						         "沙王的攻击对敌方单位注入毒液，使其移动变得迟缓，死亡时发生剧烈爆炸。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_sandking_caustic_finale_lua_Lore"							         "克里瑟历斯的毒液让受害者变得脆弱并且干涸如干旱的荒地，最后爆炸而死。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_sandking_caustic_finale_lua_caustic_finale_radius"			         "爆炸范围："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_sandking_caustic_finale_lua_caustic_finale_damage_base"		         "基础伤害："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_sandking_caustic_finale_lua_caustic_finale_damage_pct"		         "%最大生命值伤害："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_sandking_caustic_finale_lua_caustic_finale_slow"				         "%移动速度减缓："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_sandking_caustic_finale_lua_caustic_finale_duration"	                 "负面效果持续时间："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_sand_king_caustic_finale_lua_debuff"		                         "腐尸毒减速"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_sand_king_caustic_finale_lua_debuff_Description"	                 "移动速度减缓"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_leshrac_lightning_storm_lua"									"闪电风暴"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_leshrac_lightning_storm_lua_Description"						"召唤一片闪电风暴攻击目标敌方单位，并跳跃到附近的敌方单位。被攻击的敌人将会被减速。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_leshrac_lightning_storm_lua_Lore"						 	"受折磨的灵魂用来击倒敌人的闪电风暴展示了他对元素的精通。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_leshrac_lightning_storm_lua_damage"						    "伤害："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_leshrac_lightning_storm_lua_jump_count"						"闪电跳跃次数："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_leshrac_lightning_storm_lua_slow_movement_speed"		        "%移动速度减缓："
