		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_bloodstone_2"						            "血精石Ⅱ"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_bloodstone_2_Description"						"<h1>主动：血之契约</h1>%restore_duration%秒内将最大魔法值的%mana_cost_percentage%%%转化为生命恢复，同时施加弱驱散，技能吸血效果提升%lifesteal_multiplier%倍。\n<h1>被动：魔力源泉</h1>每点能量提供%regen_per_charge%点/秒的魔法回复和%amp_per_charge%%%技能增强。附近有敌方英雄阵亡时获得%kill_charges%点能量。持有者死亡时血精石失去%death_charges%点能量。具有%initial_charges_tooltip%点初始能量。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_bloodstone_2_Lore"								"血精石鲜红的色彩在战场上绝对不会被看错，拥有者似乎有无限的生命力和精力。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_bloodstone_2_bonus_health"						"+$health"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_bloodstone_2_bonus_mana"						"+$mana"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_bloodstone_2_bonus_intellect"					"+$int"
		//"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_bloodstone_bonus_magical_armor"			"%+$spell_resist"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_bloodstone_2_bonus_health_regen"				"+$hp_regen"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_bloodstone_2_spell_amp"						"%+技能增强"
		// "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_bloodstone_2_hero_lifesteal"					"%+技能吸血（英雄）"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_bloodstone_2_spell_lifesteal"					"%+技能吸血"
		// "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_bloodstone_2_creep_lifesteal"					"%+技能吸血（非英雄）"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_bloodstone_2_mana_regen_multiplier"			"%+魔法恢复增强"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_bloodstone_2_spell_lifesteal_amp"				"%+技能吸血增强"
