		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_chaos_scroll_lua"                 "混沌卷轴"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_chaos_scroll_lua_Description"     "<h1>使用:混沌重修</h1><font color='#FF7800'>随机</font>遗忘一个技能并返还技能点，然后<font color='#FF7800'>随机</font>获得一个任意技能。"

