		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tidehunter_anchor_smash_lua"										"锚击"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tidehunter_anchor_smash_lua_Description"							"潮汐猎人挥动他巨大的锚，攻击附近敌人并造成额外伤害，同时降低他们的攻击力。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tidehunter_anchor_smash_lua_Lore"									"从舰队统帅昆卡的一艘旗舰上偷来的重锚，被利维坦用作有效的近战武器。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tidehunter_anchor_smash_lua_attack_damage"						"攻击伤害加成："
		"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tidehunter_anchor_smash_lua_damage_reduction"						"%攻击力降低："
