		// "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tidehunter_anchor_smash_lua_shard_description"					"将锚击的伤害提高<font color='#B694FF'>90</font>，且使其可以影响建筑物。缩短<font color='#B694FF'>1</font>秒的冷却时间。"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_anchor_smash_reduction_lua"										"锚击"
		"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_anchor_smash_reduction_lua_Description" 							"伤害降低%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_BASEDAMAGEOUTGOING_PERCENTAGE%%%"

		"author_reply"                                                                          "作者回复"
